{
  "id": "RAW_6250e5ab",
  "title": "2026 年第一个「机皇」，粉丝先买｜三星 S26 Ultra 评测",
  "url": "https://www.ifanr.com/1657983?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=",
  "date": "2026-03-13 11:08:25",
  "author": "马扶摇",
  "siteName": "爱范儿",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>在过去的很长一段时间里，我们对于手机显示屏的追求都是非常单纯的——</p>\n  <p>不仅亮度要能在室外看得清，还得有丰富的色彩，分辨率的提升更是要跑赢通胀指数才行。</p>\n  <p>这种「既要又要还要」的精神，最终促成了如今涵盖从高端旗舰到平价中端手机的高性能 OLED 屏幕，峰值亮度、可视角度、清晰度一个不落。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657984\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-main-screen.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3000\" height=\"1688\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-main-screen.jpg!720 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-main-screen-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-main-screen-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-main-screen-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px\"></p>\n  <p>不过一块光鲜亮丽的屏幕窝在床上看电影时当然爽，可一旦需要在地铁经过体育西路的时候回复一下 boss，那些越过肩膀的视线就变得不友好起来。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657985\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-screen-peeper.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1308\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-screen-peeper.jpg!720 1308w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-screen-peeper-360x183.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-screen-peeper-768x391.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-screen-peeper-1024x521.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1308px) 100vw, 1308px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜网络</span></p>\n  <p>这也是为什么即使被批评「劣化屏幕素质」的防窥膜，依然在各种电商平台取得了不俗的销量。</p>\n  <p>而我们手里这台三星 S26 Ultra，就对这种「既要又要还要」的矛盾提出了一种解决思路——</p>\n  <p><strong>一块外表平平无奇的普通 OLED 屏幕，也能拥有超过防窥膜的隐私保护能力。</strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657986\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-display-settings.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-display-settings.jpg!720 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-display-settings-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-display-settings-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-display-settings-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px\"></p>\n  <h2>防窥：戴着镣铐跳舞</h2>\n  <p>今年 S26 Ultra 最出圈的「隐私屏幕」功能，我们已经在发布会追踪、现场上手和原理分析的文章中为大家做了详细的报道。</p>\n  <p>而当我们真正将这台浅云蓝色的 S26 Ultra 拿在手中之后，这块屏幕的防窥效果依然可以让编辑部的同事们不断发出「wow」「awesome」的声音。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657987\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-deco-with-zf7.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-deco-with-zf7.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-deco-with-zf7-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-deco-with-zf7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-deco-with-zf7-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>和爱范儿在现场体验到的功能一样，三星为 S26 Ultra 的隐私屏幕功能提供了<strong>完善的场景触发机制</strong>。</p>\n  <p>比如我们可以设置在打开系统相册、企业微信、中信银行、Gmail 和 1Password 的时候自动启用隐私屏幕。</p>\n  <p>在点开 app 的一瞬间，手机就会自动从普通模式切换为隐私屏幕，阻断来自隔壁工位的目光：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657988\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-bank-app-1.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-bank-app-1.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-bank-app-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-bank-app-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-bank-app-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>同时，也可以把 S26 Ultra 设置成只有出现通知弹窗的时候开启防窥。在你眼里一览无余的私人电话，在旁人看来就是一块巨大的黑幕：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657989\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-call-display.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-call-display.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-call-display-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-call-display-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-call-display-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>而且很多时候我们不希望别人看到的，只是屏幕上的一两处关键信息而已。</p>\n  <p>S26 Ultra 的动态防窥效果能够涵盖密码界面和通知弹窗，基本已经解决了 99% 的「突发」需求：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657990\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-message-display.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-message-display.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-message-display-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-message-display-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-message-display-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>然而就像我们在技术原理分析中指出的那样：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p>由于屏幕中有 50% 的像素为窄角发光像素，S26 Ultra 侧向亮度衰减的速率不像前代那么均匀。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657991\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-punch-compare.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-punch-compare.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-punch-compare-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-punch-compare-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-punch-compare-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\">\n   <br>\n   <span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 为了容纳广角前摄，S26 Ultra 的挖孔也变大了一些</span></p>\n  <p>但如果你想要防窥效果，给 S25 Ultra 贴了一张防窥膜的话，那 S25 Ultra 的显示效果又反过来不如 S26 Ultra 了：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657992\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-display-vs-film-front.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-display-vs-film-front.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-display-vs-film-front-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-display-vs-film-front-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-display-vs-film-front-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 贴了防窥膜的 S25 Ultra（左）</span></p>\n  <p>这也是我们在实际使用一段时间之后，对于这块硬件自带物理防窥功能的屏幕的最终结论：</p>\n  <p><strong>假如你之前有贴防窥膜的需求，那 S26 Ultra 无论打开或关闭隐私屏幕，显示效果都要好于贴上防窥膜的 S25 Ultra。</strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657993\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-display-vs-film-side.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-display-vs-film-side.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-display-vs-film-side-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-display-vs-film-side-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-display-vs-film-side-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>因此还是那句话，无论是抗反射涂层还是防窥屏，它们的重点更多都在于「硬件集成」。这种化繁为简的能力，就是新硬件最令人着迷的地方。</p>\n  <h2>系统：Bixby「倒退」九年</h2>\n  <p>今年 S26 全系列的另一大升级，就是带来了最新版本的 OneUI 8.5。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657994\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-new-system.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-new-system.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-new-system-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-new-system-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-new-system-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>相比 S25 Ultra 上面的 OneUI 8，新版本系统带来的改变非常细微。</p>\n  <p>除了电池强制显示百分比、系统界面换用胶囊形底栏，以及支持信号图标叠放之外，OneUI 8.5 本身的新东西并不算多——</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657995\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-new-status-bar.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-new-status-bar.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-new-status-bar-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-new-status-bar-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-new-status-bar-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>换言之，这依然是那个需要你熟练掌握《OneUI 使用说明书》以及 GoodLock 插件之后，才能真正用得顺心的系统。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657996\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-pen-radius.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-pen-radius.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-pen-radius-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-pen-radius-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-pen-radius-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>但在系统的微小改进之外，OneUI 8.5 其实还迎来了一个更加可感的升级：Bixby 变得更智能了。</p>\n  <p>九年前的三星 Galaxy S8 上，三星大幅提升了 Bixby 的指令处理速度和 app 功能调用能力，实现了如今难以想象的「动动嘴就能发微信红包」的效果：</p>\n  <p><img class=\" wp-image-1657997 aligncenter\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-old-bixby.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"836\" height=\"627\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-old-bixby.gif 400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-old-bixby-360x270.gif 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 836px) 100vw, 836px\"></p>\n  <p>而自那以后的 Bixby 再也没能重现那个时候的辉煌，直到最近两年 Agentic AI 概念的兴起，Bixby 才重新获得了代为操作的执行能力。</p>\n  <p>只不过在今年的国行 S26 Ultra 上，情况则变得复杂起来。</p>\n  <p>虽然三星没有介绍 Bixby 的具体「合作方」都有谁，但大概率依然是百度智能云、阿里千问、美图、生数科技等等前几年合作过的那些。</p>\n  <p>都说除了看广告还得看疗效，三星今年的新版 Bixby 的自动化体验究竟如何呢？一句话说：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><strong>一觉醒来，Bixby 能力倒退九年，还有这种好事？！</strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657998\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-bixby-command-1.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-bixby-command-1.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-bixby-command-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-bixby-command-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-bixby-command-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>从执行效果来看，目前版本 Bixby 的「智能执行」基本可以涵盖点外卖、叫车、订票、导航等等复合指令，对于各个门类下的主流 app 都实现了适配：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657999\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-mrituan-demo-2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-mrituan-demo-2.gif 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-mrituan-demo-2-360x203.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-mrituan-demo-2-768x432.gif 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"></p>\n  <p>只不过目前 Bixby 也有一些我们熟悉的问题——比如微信里，包括 Bixby 在内的所有利用无障碍权限识别屏幕画面、模拟点击的语音助手，都无法接入任何微信功能……</p>\n  <p>虽然 Gemini 已经能够通过 API 接入 + 屏幕 OCR 模拟点击的组合拳来实现不错的「智能执行」了，但在国内<strong>一边野蛮生长、一边横行霸道</strong>的软件生态里面，Bixby 就像曾经的豆包手机一样无助。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658000\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-gemini-grubhub.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1350\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-gemini-grubhub.gif 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-gemini-grubhub-360x450.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-gemini-grubhub-768x960.gif 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-gemini-grubhub-819x1024.gif 819w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"></p>\n  <p>同时，根据我们上手的体验来看，Bixby 在智能执行期间的命令区分还有一些不完善之处。</p>\n  <p>最明显的例子就是，当智能执行到某一步，Bixby 询问你的具体选择时，如果你回答不是很明确，Bixby 就会<strong>切回大语言模型</strong>帮你解释东西、而不再继续操作：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658001\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-bixby-confused.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-bixby-confused.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-bixby-confused-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-bixby-confused-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-bixby-confused-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <h2>影像：喜欢剑走偏锋</h2>\n  <p>虽然 AI 很先进，但作为一台 2026 年的旗舰超大杯，影像依旧是不得不聊的话题。</p>\n  <p>三星 S26 Ultra 搭载了一套四摄影像系统，分别是 1/1.3 英寸的两亿像素主摄、1/2.5 英寸的五千万像素超广角、1/3.94 英寸的一千万像素 3 倍长焦以及 1/2.52 英寸的五千万像素 5 倍长焦。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658002\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-back-camera.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"6192\" height=\"4128\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-back-camera.jpg!720 6192w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-back-camera-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-back-camera-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-back-camera-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 6192px) 100vw, 6192px\"></p>\n  <p>为了给这四颗镜头腾地方，S26 Ultra 在外观上做出了妥协。</p>\n  <p>它放弃了前代标志性的独立镜头排布，背部隆起了一个明显的中岛，整体设计语言全面向 Z Fold 7 看齐。</p>\n  <p>如果你曾钟情于 S25 Ultra 克制、利落的极简美学，看到这一代的背面多少会觉得有些臃肿：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658003\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-deco-compare.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-deco-compare.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-deco-compare-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-deco-compare-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-deco-compare-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>外观方面见仁见智，但突起的模组并没有让三星的硬件弯道超车。在国产品牌动辄一英寸主摄和大底长焦面前，三星的参数实在有些乏善可陈。</p>\n  <p>不过在上手后，我发现这位昔日机皇，依旧有可取之处。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658004\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/21-camera-ui.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"6192\" height=\"4128\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/21-camera-ui.jpg!720 6192w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/21-camera-ui-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/21-camera-ui-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/21-camera-ui-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 6192px) 100vw, 6192px\"></p>\n  <p>作为久被国产哈苏味、徕卡味以及蔡司味熏陶的用户，我是真不太喜欢三星偏向「保守派」的成像风格——</p>\n  <p>除了整体呈现像是没有风格的白开水，拍摄高频细节较多的场景时，自动模式总是带有较重的数码感。</p>\n  <p>但瑕不掩瑜，在传感器尺寸普遍弱于国产旗舰的情况下，我并没有觉得两者画质有明显差距。尤其是主摄上了两亿像素后，虽然像素数不完全等于画质，但在计算摄影的帮助下依旧可以有效提升成片质感。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658005\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-1-sample.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"5712\" height=\"4284\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-1-sample.jpg!720 5712w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-1-sample-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-1-sample-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-1-sample-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 5712px) 100vw, 5712px\"> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658006\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-2-sample.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4000\" height=\"3000\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-2-sample.jpg!720 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-2-sample-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-2-sample-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-2-sample-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px\"> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658007\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-3-sample.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"5712\" height=\"4284\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-3-sample.jpg!720 5712w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-3-sample-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-3-sample-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-3-sample-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 5712px) 100vw, 5712px\"> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658008\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-4-sample.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"5712\" height=\"4284\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-4-sample.jpg!720 5712w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-4-sample-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-4-sample-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-4-sample-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 5712px) 100vw, 5712px\"></p>\n  <p>不过，在光线较暗的环境下，S26 Ultra 的表现就稍微有些露怯了。</p>\n  <p>这是一张在地铁里随手抓拍的照片，此时手机并没有触发夜景模式，放大细节，车厢把手和金属环的质感其实还原得相当扎实。</p>\n  <p>但只要视线移向虚化的背景，问题就暴露了：暗部爬满了肉眼可见的底噪，甚至糊成了斑驳的色块。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658009\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-noise-sample.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"5712\" height=\"4284\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-noise-sample.jpg!720 5712w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-noise-sample-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-noise-sample-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-noise-sample-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 5712px) 100vw, 5712px\"></p>\n  <p>我们推测这主要是算法问题，三星的算法一如既往地倾向保守，似乎更想保留光线最原始的状态。</p>\n  <p>这种老派的克制当然有它的审美坚持，但代价也显而易见。所以在光线较暗的情况下，尽量手动开启夜间模式会比较稳妥：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658010\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-detailed-sample.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4000\" height=\"3000\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-detailed-sample.jpg!720 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-detailed-sample-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-detailed-sample-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-detailed-sample-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px\"></p>\n  <p>在 S26 Ultra 的长焦上，还有个细节值得注意。</p>\n  <p>不同于常见的方形潜望镜，S26 Ultra 的 5 倍长焦<strong>呈圆形开孔</strong>，结合增加的高度，基本可以判定 S26 Ultra 使用了 ALoP 技术。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658011\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-deco-marco.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"6192\" height=\"4128\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-deco-marco.jpg!720 6192w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-deco-marco-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-deco-marco-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-deco-marco-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 6192px) 100vw, 6192px\"></p>\n  <p>知名拆机频道 JerryRigEverything 也在最新的视频中证明了这一点：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658025\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-2.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4086\" height=\"2288\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-2.png!720 4086w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-2-360x202.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-2-768x430.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-2-1024x573.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4086px) 100vw, 4086px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜YouTube @JerryRigEverything</span></p>\n  <p>传统的潜望长焦像是一条横卧在手机里的长隧道，要先让棱镜将光线拐弯 90 度，再通过镜片聚焦到传感器上，会损失不少进光量：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658024\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-1.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4082\" height=\"2290\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-1.png!720 4082w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-1-360x202.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-1-768x431.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/JRE-1-1024x574.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4082px) 100vw, 4082px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜YouTube @JerryRigEverything</span></p>\n  <p>而 ALoP 将镜片组「叠」在棱镜上方，<strong>先聚光再折射</strong>，除了保护进光量之外，还能获得更自然的焦外，不会出现丑陋的方形光斑：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658026\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/good-tele-bokeh.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"6168\" height=\"5304\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/good-tele-bokeh.jpg!720 6168w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/good-tele-bokeh-360x310.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/good-tele-bokeh-768x660.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/good-tele-bokeh-1024x881.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 6168px) 100vw, 6168px\"></p>\n  <p>体验下来，我觉得照片模块最值得夸奖的，其实是仿色功能——</p>\n  <p>在滤镜列表的最前端，三星允许你上传一张准备好的照片，并根据上传的照片智能分析调色风格，实时预览到取景框中。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658012\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-color-emu.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"6192\" height=\"4128\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-color-emu.jpg!720 6192w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-color-emu-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-color-emu-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-color-emu-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 6192px) 100vw, 6192px\"></p>\n  <p>仿色是从去年开始流行的一个功能。比较主流的方式是下载修图 app，上传示意图，再上传自己拍摄的照片，修图 AI 会根据上传的示意图将照片修好。</p>\n  <p>不仅折腾不说，这种 App 往往还有次数限制，想痛快用？对不起，请充值。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658013\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-paywall.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-paywall.png!720 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-paywall-360x270.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-paywall-768x576.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-paywall-1024x768.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"></p>\n  <p>三星把这个流程直接塞进了系统相机里，确实是做了件大好事。</p>\n  <p>我尝试将一张使用富士 Negative Classic 胶片模拟拍摄的照片上传到仿色栏中，几秒之后，三星 S26 Ultra 的取景框就出现了相应的风格变化。</p>\n  <p>并且三星的仿色功能算法很巧妙，没有粗暴改变照片风格，只按照提供的照片更改了一下基调，给了一个大致的方向，以免力度过大导致画面失真。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658014\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-fuji-emulation.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4000\" height=\"3000\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-fuji-emulation.jpg!720 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-fuji-emulation-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-fuji-emulation-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-fuji-emulation-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px\"></p>\n  <p>同时 S26 Ultra 也支持你保存仿色的风格，并提供相当多的自定义选项，方便你进一步调整仿色风格。</p>\n  <p>总的来说，虽然三星仿色的还原度依旧达不到国产几家对 NC 滤镜的复刻，但强在反应迅速、可控性强，且你只要能找到对标样片，它就能仿个七七八八，给创作留出了更足的想象空间。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658015\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-night-sample-1.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"6168\" height=\"5304\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-night-sample-1.jpg!720 6168w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-night-sample-1-360x310.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-night-sample-1-768x660.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-night-sample-1-1024x881.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 6168px) 100vw, 6168px\"></p>\n  <p>不知道为什么，三星与苹果两家海外大厂，都很擅长用不那么好的硬件做出很棒的视频效果，乃至视频性能至今也是第一梯队。</p>\n  <p>三星 S26 Ultra 最高支持以 8K 30fps 的规格拍摄视频，纸面数据大家看看就好，真正让我觉得这台手机「有点东西」的，是一个叫<strong>地平线锁定</strong>的功能。</p>\n  <p>听名字你大概就能猜到它的本事：无论在拍摄时怎么晃动，或是把手机拿在手里转圈，屏幕里的画面永远稳如泰山，地平线纹丝不动。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658016\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-back-general-2.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-back-general-2.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-back-general-2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-back-general-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-back-general-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>这个功能其实不算新鲜，在其他手机上出现过，但早些年受限于芯片算力，这种模式大多是「实验室产品」——画面在剧烈晃动时会出现诡异的果冻效应。基本属于能用，但不好用。</p>\n  <p>但在 S26 Ultra 上，地平线锁定的可用性大大提升了，最高规格可以到 2560×1440 60 帧。</p>\n  <p>比如在跑动中快速翻转手机，S26 Ultra 的实时画面处理没有生硬的电子拖拽感，分辨率也保持在了足以出片的水平，表现出了极高的成熟度：</p>\n  <p><img class=\" wp-image-1658017 aligncenter\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/31-horizon-lock.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"747\" height=\"747\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/31-horizon-lock.gif 640w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/31-horizon-lock-360x360.gif 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 747px) 100vw, 747px\"></p>\n  <p>聊完拍摄，我想特别拎出来讲讲一个三星国行机型的专属功能——相框水印。</p>\n  <p>根据实测，S26 Ultra 的照片水印只能在拍摄前选择是否开启，一旦照片拍摄完毕，你没有任何办法在相册编辑里增删水印。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658018\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/32-crop-sample-2.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"6168\" height=\"5304\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/32-crop-sample-2.jpg!720 6168w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/32-crop-sample-2-360x310.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/32-crop-sample-2-768x660.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/32-crop-sample-2-1024x881.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 6168px) 100vw, 6168px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 裁剪前</span></p>\n  <p>而矛盾的是，当编辑照片的时候，无论是调整曝光与颜色，还是裁剪照片尺寸，OneUI 都知道避开水印，并根据新尺寸重新添加：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658019\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-crop-sample-2c.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"5992\" height=\"3282\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-crop-sample-2c.jpg!720 5992w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-crop-sample-2c-360x197.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-crop-sample-2c-768x421.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-crop-sample-2c-1024x561.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 5992px) 100vw, 5992px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 裁剪后</span></p>\n  <p>也就是说，S26 Ultra 在拍摄后是可以识别到水印存在的，但<strong>买定离手</strong>、拍完不给添加或者删除。</p>\n  <p>智能了，但只有一点点。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658020\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-smart.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3848\" height=\"2006\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-smart.jpg!720 3848w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-smart-360x188.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-smart-768x400.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-smart-1024x534.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3848px) 100vw, 3848px\"></p>\n  <h2>结语：粉丝先买</h2>\n  <p>作为 2026 年第一批直板旗舰，三星 S26 Ultra 除了本身作为商品之外，也是让我们看到了三星显示在屏幕技术方面的突破。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658021\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/35-back-general.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/35-back-general.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/35-back-general-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/35-back-general-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/35-back-general-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>虽然如今在国内的市占率和知名度都排不上号，但无论是 HPX 系列传感器，还是依旧稳居供应链顶端的屏幕，三星又一直是国产手机绕不过去的一个环节。</p>\n  <p>只不过，单从产品力上看，S26 Ultra 给人的感觉并不安稳。</p>\n  <p>毕竟和前几代机型相比，S26 Ultra 的防窥硬件，的确影响到了一些屏幕观感、亮度和抗眩光强度。</p>\n  <p>而防窥膜虽然是很多人的刚需，但不要防窥的用户同样数不胜数——</p>\n  <p><strong>这种「为了细节功能代替用户做出取舍」，可能会成为这一代三星最大的障碍。</strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1658022\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/36-buds-4-pro.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/36-buds-4-pro.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/36-buds-4-pro-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/36-buds-4-pro-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/36-buds-4-pro-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>因此，对坚持至今的 S21 Ultra、S22 Ultra 用户来说，S26 Ultra 无疑是全方位的进步，可以不用犹豫、直接换新。</p>\n  <p><strong>然而对 S24 Ultra、S25 Ultra 以及持观望态度的潜在用户们来说，S26 Ultra 在木桶各块板子上的取舍并不平均，很难形成足够的说服力。</strong></p>\n  <p>总之，对于这样一台 12+256GB 起步价 9999 元人民币的手机来说，还是让粉丝先买吧。</p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文是对三星 S26 Ultra 的深度评测，重点分析了其硬件级隐私防窥屏、基于 Agentic AI 的 Bixby 自动化能力以及 ALoP 影像技术，并对其市场定位给出了谨慎建议。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文是对三星 S26 Ultra 的深度评测，重点分析了其硬件级隐私防窥屏、基于 Agentic AI 的 Bixby 自动化能力以及 ALoP 影像技术，并对其市场定位给出了谨慎建议。",
  "summary": "文章详细评估了 2026 年三星旗舰 S26 Ultra。核心亮点在于其创新的「隐私屏幕」，通过硬件集成实现超越防窥膜的效果，并支持场景化自动触发，但也因此在屏幕亮度和均匀性上做出了取舍。系统方面，OneUI 8.5 推动 Bixby 向 AI Agent 演进，实现了跨 App 的复合指令执行，但在国内生态下仍面临兼容性挑战。影像系统引入 ALoP 技术优化长焦进光量与虚化，并新增实用的系统级「仿色」功能。作者认为，尽管技术有突破，但 9999 元的高昂起步价和特定功能的权衡，使其更适合忠实粉丝或老用户升级。",
